about.description:
The Stackdriver Trace API sends application trace data to Stackdriver Trace for viewing. Trace data is collected for all App Engine applications by default. Trace data from other applications can be provided using this API.
See the [quick start guide](https://googleapis.dev/python/cloudtrace/latest/index.html#quick-start).
about.summary: Google Cloud Trace API client library

name: google-cloud-trace
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "google-cloud-trace" %}
{% set version = "1.12.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/google-cloud-trace-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 22f6ccc476ce3101d41fbabceac3fefcdfe057d2967b3e8e20c02671363a524a

build:
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.7
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.7
    - google-api-core-grpc >=1.34.0,<3.0.0dev,!=2.0.*,!=2.1.*,!=2.2.*,!=2.3.*,!=2.4.*,!=2.5.*,!=2.6.*,!=2.7.*,!=2.8.*,!=2.9.*,!=2.10.*
    - proto-plus >=1.22.0,<2.0.0dev
    - protobuf >=3.19.5,<5.0.0dev,!=3.20.0,!=3.20.1,!=4.21.0,!=4.21.1,!=4.21.2,!=4.21.3,!=4.21.4,!=4.21.5

test:
  imports:
    - grpc
    - google.cloud.trace
    - google.cloud.trace_v1
    - google.cloud.trace_v2
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/googleapis/python-trace
  summary: Google Cloud Trace API client library
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: Apache
  license_file: LICENSE
  description: "The Stackdriver Trace API sends application trace data to Stackdriver Trace for viewing. Trace data is collected for all App Engine applications by default. Trace data from other applications can be provided using this API.\nSee the [quick start guide](https://googleapis.dev/python/cloudtrace/latest/index.html#quick-start)."

  doc_url: https://cloud.google.com/python/docs/reference/cloudtrace/latest
  dev_url: https://github.com/googleapis/google-cloud-python/tree/main/packages/google-cloud-trace

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - xylar
    - parthea
